QuestData.Title: Wind Trader Lathrai
QuestData.Description: I was asked to pick up and deliver some boxes of goods from an ethereal in Shattrath City.$B$BLast I saw him, he was standing outside of the World's End Tavern in Lower City. His name is Wind Trader Lathrai, and that's all that I know!$B$BWant more answers, go talk with him!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Wind Trader Lathrai near the World's End Tavern in the Lower City section of Shattrath City.
QuestData.RewardText: Yes? How may I help you today, $r?
